meanings.definition: A barangay in the municipality of Porac, Pampanga, Philippines.
meanings.english_definition: A barangay in the municipality of Porac, Pampanga, Philippines.

examples.sentence: Camuning is one of the barangays in Porac that was affected by the lahar flows.
